ZH: 1. 我们需要对这个项目投入更多的时间和精力。
EN: We need to invest more time and effort into this project.
ZH: 2. 这位医生对他的工作非常投入。
EN: This doctor is very dedicated to his work.
ZH: 3. 她投入了许多金钱来支持慈善事业。
EN: She has invested a lot of money to support charity.
ZH: 4. 很多人错把投入和回报混淆了。
EN: Many people confuse investment with returns.
ZH: 5. 我们需要提高对教育的投入。
EN: We need to increase investment in education.
ZH: 6. 他对体育活动的投入使他成为了优秀的运动员。
EN: His dedication to sports has made him an outstanding athlete.
ZH: 7. 这个项目需要大量的资金投入。
EN: This project requires a substantial financial investment.
ZH: 8. 她对她的梦想投入了全部的心血。
EN: She has put all her efforts into pursuing her dream.
ZH: 9. 投入这个行业需要一定的技术知识和经验。
EN: Entering this industry requires certain technical knowledge and experience.
ZH: 10. 投入市场竞争需要有强大的竞争力。
EN: To enter the market competition, one needs to be highly competitive.
ZH: 11. 他投入了所有的精力来照顾病重的母亲。
EN: He devoted all his energy to taking care of his critically ill mother.
ZH: 12. 这个计划需要大量资源的投入。
EN: This plan requires a significant investment of resources.
ZH: 13. 她对音乐的投入让她成为一位出色的歌手。
EN: Her dedication to music has made her an excellent singer.
ZH: 14. 他对新技术非常投入，经常在自己的业余时间进行研究。
EN: He is very committed to new technologies and often conducts research in his spare time.
ZH: 15. 在这个领域取得成功需要付出很大的投入。
EN: Achieving success in this field requires a significant investment.
ZH: 16. 我们应该逐步增加对可再生能源的投入。
EN: We should gradually increase investment in renewable energy.
ZH: 17. 他们的团队以其高度的投入和合作精神而闻名。
EN: Their team is known for its high dedication and spirit of cooperation.
ZH: 18. 为了提升自己的技能，他不断投入时间和金钱进行进修。
EN: In order to improve his skills, he constantly invests time and money in further education.
ZH: 19. 这次投资的投入与收益将在未来几年内显现出来。
EN: The investment in this venture will yield returns in the coming years.
ZH: 20. 对于创业者而言，将自己的资金投入到新项目中是一种冒险。
EN: For entrepreneurs, investing their own money in a new project is a gamble.
